					<description><![CDATA[<p>“Neumorphism融合了Skeuomorphism和平面设计技术。就像拟态（Skeoumorphism）&#8230; <a class="more-link" href="https://www.latika.guru/neumorphism-keyboard%e6%8b%9f%e7%89%a9%e9%a3%8e%e6%a0%bc%e9%94%ae%e7%9b%98css%e5%88%86%e4%ba%ab/">继续阅读<span class="screen-reader-text">Neumorphism Keyboard拟物风格键盘</span></a></p>
<p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.latika.guru/neumorphism-keyboard%e6%8b%9f%e7%89%a9%e9%a3%8e%e6%a0%bc%e9%94%ae%e7%9b%98css%e5%88%86%e4%ba%ab/">Neumorphism Keyboard拟物风格键盘</a>最先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.latika.guru">Latika Blog</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: left;">“Neumorphism融合了Skeuomorphism和平面设计技术。就像拟态（Skeoumorphism）一样，它是一种现实主义风格，它模仿真实对象并在数字环境中创建它们的3D表示。拟物化是值得探索的风格。它时尚，细致，使用它进行设计确实很有趣。”</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">今天分享一个使用CSS创作Neumorphic元素的示例，一个很好的学习CSS布局的例子，值得借鉴+记录一下（404PTSD综合症犯了，马上搬过来再说。）</p>
<h3>HTML</h3>
<pre class="EnlighterJSRAW" data-enlighter-language="generic">&lt;div class="keyboard"&gt;

&lt;section class="key-row"&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;~&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;1&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;2&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;3&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;4&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;5&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;6&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;7&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;8&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;9&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;0&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;-&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;=&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key two"&gt;backspace&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
  
&lt;section class="key-row"&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one-one-half l"&gt;tab&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;q&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;w&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;e&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;r&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;t&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;y&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;u&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;i&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;o&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;p&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;[&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;]&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;\&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
  
&lt;section class="key-row"&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one-one-half l"&gt;search&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;a&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;s&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;d&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;f&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;g&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;h&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;j&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;k&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;l&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;'&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key two r"&gt;enter&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
  
&lt;section class="key-row"&gt;
  &lt;div class="key two-two-half l"&gt;shift&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;z&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;x&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;c&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;v&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;b&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;n&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;m&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;/&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key two-two-half r"&gt;shift&lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;/section&gt;
    
&lt;section class="key-row"&gt;
  &lt;div class="key two l"&gt;ctrl&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key two l"&gt;alt&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key five"&gt;&lt;!-- Spacebar --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one-one-half"&gt;alt&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="key one"&gt;ctrl&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="arrowkey-container two-two-half"&gt;
  
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
  
&lt;/div&gt;
  
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>
<h3>CSS</h3>
<pre class="EnlighterJSRAW" data-enlighter-language="css">* { box-sizing:border-box; }

@import url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300,400,600);

body {
  background:#aaa;
  font:300 15px/24px "Open Sans", sans-serif;
  color:#bbb;
  user-select:none;
  text-shadow:0 0 1px #aaa;
}

h1 { font-size:5em; line-height:1.5; }

.keyboard {
  margin:30px auto;
  width:90%;
  height:400px;
  background:#bbb;
  padding:30px 80px;
  border-radius:10px;
  border-bottom:6px solid #999;
}

.key-row {
  display:-webkit-flex;
  margin:0 auto 7px;
  line-height:50px;
}

.key, .arrowkey-container {
   margin:0 6px 0 0; 
  text-align:center;
}

.key { 
  background:#444;
  color:#eee;
  border-radius:4px;
  box-shadow:0 1px 0 #222, inset 0 1px 3px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  transition:0.1s;
  align-items:center;
  align-content:center;
  height:57px;
  border:2px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  cursor:pointer;
}

sup, sub { outline:1px solid magenta; display:block; align-self:center; }

.key:active { transform:translateY(1px); background:#333; box-shadow:0 1px 0 #000;}

.one { flex:1; } /* one */
.one-one-half { flex:1.5; } /* One and one half */
.two { flex:2; } /* two */
.two-two-half { flex:2.5; } /* Two and two half */
.three { flex:3; } /* three */
.five { flex:5; }

.key-row .key:last-child { margin:0; }

.l { text-align:left; padding-left:12px; }
.r { text-align:right; padding-right:12px; }</pre>
<p>Flexbox Keyboard：<a href="https://codepen.io/bennettfeely/pen/DgbrLG" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://codepen.io/bennettfeely/pen/DgbrLG</a></p>
